      getline(std::basic_istream< CharT, Traits > & is, 
              basic_string< CharT, Traits, Allocator > & s);
    template<typename Ch, typename Allocator> 
      std::size_t hash_value(basic_string< Ch, std::char_traits< Ch >, Allocator > const & v);
  }
